In dom all html elements are defined as objects.
Properties: is a value that you can set to the objects(like changing content of an html element).
Methods:an action.(like add or delete).
Methods of document object: 
Getting element:
Getting an element by id
Getting an element by class
Returns all elements heving same class.
Getting an element by tagname
Getting an element by query selector
